{"tid":505234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【濃霧中叛逃】再有北韓士兵越過休戰區 逃到南韓變節","createTime":"2017-12-21T01:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T01:45:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"176f9f75c02ddc917c40bdfdce72f233cfa2e036","tid":505234,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T01:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171221/large/1513818618_0d60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171221%2Flarge%2F1513818618_0d60.jpg&h=4880ac24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再有北韓士兵變節，南韓國防部指，一名北韓士兵周四早上越過南北韓邊境非軍事區（DMZ）投奔南韓。<br />\n<br />\n國防部發言人指，變節的北韓士兵是基層人員，在當地時間周四早上8時04分(本港7時04分)，在濃霧中越過邊境逃到南韓。雙方未開一槍。這是五個星期內，第二宗類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n11月中一名北韓士兵越過休戰區兩韓邊境投奔南韓，北韓士兵猛烈開火阻止，他身中5槍受重傷，事發後北韓已撤換了板門店共同警備區的所有警備兵力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171221/57608311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608311&d=Lae4Q969r7wfmezT87%2Byq9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=5b58a439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57608311&h=4a9835f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171221/57608311</a>"}]}